{"tid":1202272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"‎【反送中】集思廣益 今晚之後會點發展 有咩對策良計","createTime":"2019-06-11T08:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T08:40:08.000Z","uid":102005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"642db795f29b72c8c1c04560d3bac82190f805bc","tid":1202272,"uid":102005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"唔會一下沖完就港共屈服<br />\n應該準備進入長期不合作運動<br />\n大家有咩好計 拋定D 出黎先<br />\n同埋我認為要諗定worst case scenario 到時唔work 就去下一步<br />\n唔係企係龍和on99 俾人驅趕完就唔知做咩野<br />\n下一站禮賓府定領事館之類<br />\n<br />\nE.g.<br />\n游擊式於港島各處佔領要道及迴旋處, 每每20-30人行動 遇警即四散<br />\n使警方疲於奔命四處驅趕 造成連鐶式車塞車局面<br />\n加上號召壞車及慢駛活動, 基乎癱瘓港島路面交通<br />\n<br />\n中區環球大廈對開迴旋處塞車嚴重 交通警員在場指揮 [2019-01-21]<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1439195-20190121.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1439195-20190121.htm&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAoy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=f9dcdd5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1439195-20190121.htm&h=7ef5cc26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1439195-20190121.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n荃灣九巴壞車塞迴旋處 麗城交通嚴重擠塞 [2019-01-25]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/287319/%E5%87%BA%E9%96%80%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%9E%E8%BB%8A%E5%A1%9E%E8%BF%B4%E6%97%8B%E8%99%95-%E9%BA%97%E5%9F%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E6%93%A0%E5%A1%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F287319%2F%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2584%258F-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25A1%259E%25E8%25BF%25B4%25E6%2597%258B%25E8%2599%2595-%25E9%25BA%2597%25E5%259F%258E%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2593%25A0%25E5%25A1%259E&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAoy